Package smarthome.domain.house.vo

Class Address

java.lang.Object
smarthome.domain.house.vo.Address
All Implemented Interfaces:
ValueObject
public class Address extends Object implements ValueObject
Represents an Address in the domain. An Address is a value object that consists of a StreetName, StreetNumber, ZipCode, City and Country.
